      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "难得啊，那么早起来跟我打招呼",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "终于不是只有晚上见了",
