      "content": "只是外貌的话不至于",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你觉得你算帅的吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "你觉得呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "？我在问你，你干嘛反问我？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "帅不帅男人自己说了不算啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "给女生认可",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh上道啊哥们",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "你确实还挺帅的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "我知道",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "不愧是我",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "???你不担心我说你油腻吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "我真的很想这么说你，你要是觉得我油腻，我也没招了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "“没有帅哥不知道自己帅，除非他是装的”",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以你是从什么时候知道自己长得帅的？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "照镜子的时候",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "【捂脸别打我】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "开玩笑的，我不需要通过照镜子，从小到大，别人的眼神就会告诉我",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "我真服了，你也太自恋了吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "你不担心女孩子下头吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "我只跟你这么说，因为你这么问了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "要是其他女生也这么问你？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "没有其他女生这么问过",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "他们不是你这样的性格的话，我或许也不会搭理她们",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得和你实话实说，你不会反感",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "你很看重脸吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "你觉得自己长得帅有优势吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "大概学生上我们的课不会觉得太乏味，就算我讲的内容无聊，他们也可以看我的脸？Wait",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "不是，你怎么越想越自恋了，你不会不好意思吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "陈述事实",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是长相对我而言不是最重要的，对我的生活没有太多的加持",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "这也不是我追求的，所以我承认就承认啊，我觉得不会影响我的人性",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "只有那些明知道自己长得很帅，想从中谋取红利的人，才会不承认自己长得帅，假装浑然不觉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "你对自己的同性分析的很透彻",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "分析人物心理也是学文学的重要一环",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh说的我好像是一个观察者",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "好了，不扯这个帅不帅的，没意思",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "明天北京就要降温了，你那里呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "哦，原来你是北京人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "我突然想到我们好像聊了，都没有交换彼此的彼此的基础信息",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你也没问我是哪里的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为我觉得不重要",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "对了，我不是北京的，我只是在北京工作",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "我是浙江舟山人，你呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "苏州人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "山水园林好地方",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "阖闾城碧铺秋草，乌鹊桥红带夕阳。处处楼前飘管吹，家家门外泊舟航。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "你写的诗？？？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "这要是我写的诗，我现在应该被文坛供起来",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "白居易写的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "哦哦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "我还以为你第一反应是玩散装江苏",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "居然念段古诗，果然是教汉语言文学的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "散装江苏的梗，人人都在玩，很无聊啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "我要是也玩，人人都玩那个，那我也会很无聊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "然后你就念了一段诗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "来凸显自己的与众不同吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "你就这么水灵灵的说出来了，不担心我觉得你装叉吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "不担心",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为我的脑回路确实挺装hhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "自古以来，文人墨客风雅的驱动力一定都有装吧？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "你的意思是你学文学也是为了装吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "这个阶段好像是反复的，就像钟摆一样来回摇晃",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "一开始是为了装，后来是为了装，过程中 又有一部分是装",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "我怀疑你讲这段话也是为了装，因为我根本听不懂。Ok？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "你专门把话讲成别人听不懂的样子，就是为了装叉吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh那你喜欢找挑我的毛病是因为爱玩找茬吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "才不是嘞",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "真的全是槽点，不吐槽忍不住啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你应该上吐槽大会",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "你自己不也是爱吐槽吗？你还说我",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "那我们半斤对8两，50步笑50步可以吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "嘿，老师被我抓到了一个错，是50笑100步",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "在古代1斤斤是16两，半斤对半斤。8两和半斤对得工整，所以50步和50步就更工整啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "你不觉得这样对称说起来更顺口，更合理吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "服了，又给你找到一个装叉机会",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "我就不该问，烦死了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "【森贝尔跳舞】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "我平常还真没这么装叉。一开口就是什么风花雪月掉书袋，我感觉和你这样说话特别有意思",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为你的反应真的很大",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "但其实讲实话，我这种心理很像是小学时爱抓女同学辫子的垃圾男生，还以为自己很有趣",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "你要是生气了，你就把我当做乐子吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "其实...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也觉得我每次吐槽你，你反应都很大，也很有意思",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "是我在玩你好吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh笑死",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "那我们这是碟中谍",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "我刚想说北京降温了，你们苏州降温了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "昨天还是十几度，今天一下就变冷了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你进出要注意保暖",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "?突如其来的温情?",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "搞什么啊？你不是这挂的吧？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh好，好好，是我装的，假装关心你",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "刚刚去买吃的，经过小巷，太冷了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "风太大了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "决定今天晚上一定要把罗拉快跑看完",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:05",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "[下定决心]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，应该来得及",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:21",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "时间不算晚，应该不会睡着",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "你在忙什么呢？那么晚才回复",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "刚和一个泰国小朋友聊了会天，关心一下最近的学业进展",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "？？？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "哥们在泰国还有业务呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "搞电信诈骗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "我要是说出具体情况，我担心你会夜里醒来扇自己两巴掌",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "怎么说？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "说来话长，我尽量长话短说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你还是别说了，我嫌啰嗦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "你还是让我说了吧，我都打好草稿了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "不说就白费了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "5年前我被教育部派去泰国教中文，算是义务教学持，国家之间的帮扶",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "在那里我认识一个很好学的男生，学习进行到一半的时候，他的父亲因为诈骗不知所踪，母亲也重病。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "于是他只好辍学去打工，他家里有个小妹妹，很向往中国，很希望能够学好中文，以前经常时不时来学校听课",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为他的哥哥无论如何都要去工作养家了，希望他的妹妹能够继续学业",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "我那时候学也快要结束了，要回国了，我跟他哥哥商量了一下，就资助他的妹妹",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "难得有这样的哥哥",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "而且还是在泰国这样的国家，愿意让妹妹继续读书",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "是啊，我很感动",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "知道，读书是条出路的。贫苦人家的泰国孩子真的是凤毛麟角",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "尤其他还是男的，愿意给妹妹去挣钱，这真的更罕见了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "那妹妹现在多大？她应该很感激你吧。？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "现在上初二",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "我倒是不需要她感激我",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "成绩好吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "中上游水平",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "哥哥在外面打工挣钱养家，但家里的母亲还是需要妹妹照顾",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "妹妹无法全身心的投入到学习里面，有这样的成绩已经很不错了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "我还以为这样的孩子会发奋读书，读到年级top3",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "你说的是新闻和影视剧里的主角 ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "普通人在一团乱麻中的家庭能够保持向学的心就已经非常了不起了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也不求他能考到年级前几啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "还要每天回家做饭。给妈妈擦拭身体，能到这个成绩已经很棒了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "就算不论成绩有这份坚持和面对困境的能力",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "我相信妹妹以后也会成长为很优秀的人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "对了，她有名字，她叫阿南雅。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "泰国名字？是什么意思？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "勇敢的，善良的，充满希望的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "cao",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "好贴切啊！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "是啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也这么觉得，妹妹对于他们整个家庭而言就是希望",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "不过才初二背负那么多，会不会很累啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "这个问题我之前也和哥哥讨论过",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "没有办法的，生活在那样的国家，又是那样悲剧的家庭",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "没有一条路走已是万幸，。就算身上背着重担也要往前跑",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "阿南雅和哥哥都是知足的人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也和他们说了，不要把我的帮助当成一种负担",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "我不帮他们也会帮别人的，或许别人做的不一定有他们好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "哎",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "他们爸爸找得到吗？？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "就这么人间蒸发了，是死是活，知道吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "不知道",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "警方那边也没什么下落",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "你知道前段时间太子集团被捣毁了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "对啊，这个我知道，好像在b站刷到过",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "是说第一大诈骗集团对吧？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "当时看到这个新闻时，我马上去找阿南雅哥哥l ",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为他们的父亲也有可能是去了柬埔寨。不过很可惜，这次警方的行动中，抓捕的人员没有他的父亲",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "怎么感觉跟写小说一样？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "好不真实，好魔幻",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "对于我们这些身在和平国家的人来说，确实难以想象",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "但在他们的世界中，父亲消失人间正在很常见",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "我那时教导学生中不只有阿南雅一家的父亲参与诈骗，人间蒸发",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "但只有阿南雅的哥哥选择让妹妹继续读书",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "这就是命运吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "我不愿意称这位命中注定，似乎画上了句号，永远不能翻盘",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得这只是国家的环境导致的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "如果我和阿南雅的哥哥换了出生的国家，或许我现在承担的就是他那样的角色",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "那出生在哪里，成为哪一国的人，这不就是命运吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "就像我们生活在中国，也有贫富的差距",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "出生在有钱人家和普通人家就是两种命运啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "你就当我钻牛角尖，钻文字眼吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "我想说这是起点不同",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "虽然起点不同，但都可以往前跑的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "虽然都往前跑，但有的人出生就在罗马啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "你觉得他们还需要跑吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "我管那些身在罗马的人跑不跑？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "只要地狱里的人能跑出来就行了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "你说老师你还真别说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "你真的有点东西",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，我也么觉得",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "【我骄傲】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "不行了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "，我决定再也不夸你了，夸你两句你就喘上了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "22:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "我没有蹬鼻子上脸吧？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "我只是恰好的认清了自己",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "【得意】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "好了，聊了那么久，你有没有去看电影啊？都快11点了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "22:51"
    },
    {
